**Additional Protections**:

- **Webpack/build integration**: Configure your bundler to inject nonces at build time using `__webpack_nonce__`
- **Gradual rollout**: Use `Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only` first to identify issues before enforcing
- **Trusted Types**: Add `require-trusted-types-for 'script'` for DOM XSS protection in modern browsers
- **Subresource Integrity (SRI)**: Add integrity hashes for CDN resources:
```html
<script src="https://cdn.example.com/lib.js" 
