        crossorigin="anonymous"
        nonce="${nonce}">
</script>
```
- **Regular CSP auditing**: Use tools like Google's CSP Evaluator (https://csp-evaluator.withgoogle.com/) to validate your policy

Using 'unsafe-inline' in your Content Security Policy completely undermines XSS protection - it's one of the most common CSP misconfigurations that led to major breaches like the British Airways Magecart attack.

